GFT, A Go language tab formatting tool.

- Replace all tabs in the go file with Spaces
- Default is 4 Spaces

Before:

func foo() {
        for i := 0; i < 100; i++ {
                println(i)
        }
}

After:

func foo() {
    for i := 0; i < 100; i++ {
        println(i)
    }
}

Install:

    > g++ -std=c++17 -Os gft.cc -o gft
    > upx gft

Or go to download page: https://gft.bingxio.fun/

Usage:

    > gft <FILE | DIR> | <Spaces>
    > gft v

